description:
Ep 16: Turning Down the Crown
The ladies plan for Puerto Rico, but exclude Carlton after more mysterious incidents.

Kyle and Joyce decide not to invite Carlton on their Puerto Rico trip, especially after Kyle reveals how she received strange, spooky words on her computer screen saver. Brandi tries to avoid Lisa at Gigi's glamorous going-away party. Kyle mistakenly reveals to the group that Joyce's father has died and Joyce feels betrayed.
